      </biblio>

      <biblio type="raw" xml:id="R-webshot2">
        Chang, Winston (2025). <title>webshot2: Take Screenshots of Web Pages</title>. R package version 0.1.2. <url href="https://rstudio.github.io/webshot2/"/>.
